                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="ar-Latn-x-lc" key="work_7759">ʿUmdat al-fuḥūl fi šarḥ al-Fuṣūl</title>
                     <title xml:lang="ar" key="work_7759">عمدة الفحول في شرح الفصول</title>
                     <title xml:lang="en" type="desc" key="work_7759">Support of the Paragons to Comment on the AphorismsSupport of the Paragons to Comment on the Aphorisms</title>
                     <note>Original manuscript in Veliyeddin Efendi.</note>
                     <note>This is a lemmatically arranged commentary. The introduction begins on <locus>f. 103b</locus>; the beginning of each Book is as follows: Bk1: 103b; Bk2: 113b; Bk3: 122b; Bk4: 129b; Bk5: 141b; Bk6: 151a; Bk7: 158b.</note>
